</code></pre></div></div><div class="print:hidden" data-fade-overlay="true" aria-hidden="true" style="--fade-color-light:#ffffff;--fade-color-dark:#0B0C0E"></div></div><div data-state="inactive" data-orientation="horizontal" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-_R_1r8elmjlfium6abasnpfiulb_-trigger-1" hidden="" id="radix-_R_1r8elmjlfium6abasnpfiulb_-content-1" tabindex="-1" class="w-full min-w-full max-w-full h-full max-h-full relative [&amp;_[data-component-part=code-block-root]]:!rounded-xt"></div><div data-state="inactive" data-orientation="horizontal" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-_R_1r8elmjlfium6abasnpfiulb_-trigger-2" hidden="" id="radix-_R_1r8elmjlfium6abasnpfiulb_-content-2" tabindex="-1" class="w-full min-w-full max-w-full h-full max-h-full relative [&amp;_[data-component-part=code-block-root]]:!rounded-xt"></div><div data-state="inactive" data-orientation="horizontal" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-_R_1r8elmjlfium6abasnpfiulb_-trigger-3" hidden="" id="radix-_R_1r8elmjlfium6abasnpfiulb_-content-3" tabindex="-1" class="w-full min-w-full max-w-full h-full max-h-full relative [&amp;_[data-component-part=code-block-root]]:!rounded-xt"></div><div data-state="inactive" data-orientation="horizontal" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="radix-_R_1r8elmjlfium6abasnpfiulb_-trigger-4" hidden="" id="radix-_R_1r8elmjlfium6abasnpfiulb_-content-4" tabindex="-1" class="w-full min-w-full max-w-full h-full max-h-full relative [&amp;_[data-component-part=code-block-root]]:!rounded-xt"></div></div></div><div class="callout my-4 px-5 py-4 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl flex gap-3 border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50 dark:border-blue-900 dark:bg-blue-600/20" data-callout-type="note"><div class="mt-0.5 w-4" data-component-part="callout-icon"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-4 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300" aria-label="Note"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 1.3C10.14 1.3 12.7 3.86 12.7 7C12.7 10.14 10.14 12.7 7 12.7C5.48908 12.6974 4.0408 12.096 2.97241 11.0276C1.90403 9.9592 1.30264 8.51092 1.3 7C1.3 3.86 3.86 1.3 7 1.3ZM7 0C3.14 0 0 3.14 0 7C0 10.86 3.14 14 7 14C10.86 14 14 10.86 14 7C14 3.14 10.86 0 7 0ZM8 3H6V8H8V3ZM8 9H6V11H8V9Z"></path></svg></div><div class="text-sm prose dark:prose-invert min-w-0 w-full [&amp;_kbd]:bg-background-light dark:[&amp;_kbd]:bg-background-dark [&amp;_code]:!text-current [&amp;_kbd]:!text-current [&amp;_a]:!text-current [&amp;_a]:border-current [&amp;_strong]:!text-current text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300" data-component-part="callout-content"><span data-as="p">Without a type prefix, the API will auto-detect the identifier type by order (domain → ticker → isin → crypto).</span></div></div></div></div></div><div id="" role="listitem" class="step group/step step-container relative flex items-start pb-5"><div data-component-part="step-line" class="absolute w-px h-[calc(100%-2.75rem)] top-[2.75rem] bg-gray-200/70 dark:bg-white/10" contentEditable="false"></div><div class="absolute ml-[-13px] py-2" data-component-part="step-number" contentEditable="false"><div class="relative size-7 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/10 text-xs text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 font-semibold flex items-center justify-center"><div class="">2</div><div class="absolute" data-component-part="step-number-anchor-link"><a href="#" class="flex items-center opacity-0 border-0" aria-label="Navigate to header"><div class="w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="gray" height="12px" viewBox="0 0 576 512"><path d="M0 256C0 167.6 71.6 96 160 96h72c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H160C98.1 144 48 194.1 48 256s50.1 112 112 112h72c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H160C71.6 416 0 344.4 0 256zm576 0c0 88.4-71.6 160-160 160H344c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24h72c61.9 0 112-50.1 112-112s-50.1-112-112-112H344c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24h72c88.4 0 160 71.6 160 160zM184 232H392c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H184c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24z"></path></svg></div></a></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-hidden pl-8 pr-px"><p class="mt-2 font-semibold prose dark:prose-invert text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200" contentEditable="false" data-component-part="step-title">Register an account and get your Client ID</p><div data-component-part="step-content" class="prose dark:prose-invert"><div class="callout my-4 px-5 py-4 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl flex gap-3 border border-green-200 bg-green-50 dark:border-green-900 dark:bg-green-600/20 [&amp;_[data-component-part=&#x27;callout-icon&#x27;]]:mt-px" data-callout-type="tip"><div class="mt-0.5 w-4" data-component-part="callout-icon"><svg width="11" height="14" viewBox="0 0 11 14" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-green-800 dark:text-green-300 w-3.5 h-auto" aria-label="Tip"><path d="M3.12794 12.4232C3.12794 12.5954 3.1776 12.7634 3.27244 12.907L3.74114 13.6095C3.88471 13.8248 4.21067 14 4.46964 14H6.15606C6.41415 14 6.74017 13.825 6.88373 13.6095L7.3508 12.9073C7.43114 12.7859 7.49705 12.569 7.49705 12.4232L7.50055 11.3513H3.12521L3.12794 12.4232ZM5.31288 0C2.52414 0.00875889 0.5 2.26889 0.5 4.78826C0.5 6.00188 0.949566 7.10829 1.69119 7.95492C2.14321 8.47011 2.84901 9.54727 3.11919 10.4557C3.12005 10.4625 3.12175 10.4698 3.12261 10.4771H7.50342C7.50427 10.4698 7.50598 10.463 7.50684 10.4557C7.77688 9.54727 8.48281 8.47011 8.93484 7.95492C9.67728 7.13181 10.1258 6.02703 10.1258 4.78826C10.1258 2.15486 7.9709 0.000106649 5.31288 0ZM7.94902 7.11267C7.52078 7.60079 6.99082 8.37878 6.6077 9.18794H4.02051C3.63739 8.37878 3.10743 7.60079 2.67947 7.11294C2.11997 6.47551 1.8126 5.63599 1.8126 4.78826C1.8126 3.09829 3.12794 1.31944 5.28827 1.3126C7.2435 1.3126 8.81315 2.88226 8.81315 4.78826C8.81315 5.63599 8.50688 6.47551 7.94902 7.11267ZM4.87534 2.18767C3.66939 2.18767 2.68767 3.16939 2.68767 4.37534C2.68767 4.61719 2.88336 4.81288 3.12521 4.81288C3.36705 4.81288 3.56274 4.61599 3.56274 4.37534C3.56274 3.6515 4.1515 3.06274 4.87534 3.06274C5.11719 3.06274 5.31288 2.86727 5.31288 2.62548C5.31288 2.38369 5.11599 2.18767 4.87534 2.18767Z"></path></svg></div><div class="text-sm prose dark:prose-invert min-w-0 w-full [&amp;_kbd]:bg-background-light dark:[&amp;_kbd]:bg-background-dark [&amp;_code]:!text-current [&amp;_kbd]:!text-current [&amp;_a]:!text-current [&amp;_a]:border-current [&amp;_strong]:!text-current text-green-800 dark:text-green-300" data-component-part="callout-content"><span data-as="p">Logo API is free to use and <u>we don’t ask for any attribution</u>.</span></div></div><span data-as="p">Each request must include your unique client ID. This ensures your usage stays within fair limits and logos render reliably.</span><span data-as="p">To get your client ID, register for free from our <a href="https://developers.brandfetch.com/register" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="link">Developer Portal</a>.</span></div></div></div><div id="" role="listitem" class="step group/step step-container relative flex items-start pb-5"><div data-component-part="step-line" class="absolute w-px h-[calc(100%-2.75rem)] top-[2.75rem] bg-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-200 dark:from-white/10 via-80% to-transparent group-has-[[data-component-part=&quot;step-content&quot;]:empty]/step:hidden" contentEditable="false"></div><div class="absolute ml-[-13px] py-2" data-component-part="step-number" contentEditable="false"><div class="relative size-7 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/10 text-xs text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 font-semibold flex items-center justify-center"><div class="">3</div><div class="absolute" data-component-part="step-number-anchor-link"><a href="#" class="flex items-center opacity-0 border-0" aria-label="Navigate to header"><div class="w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="gray" height="12px" viewBox="0 0 576 512"><path d="M0 256C0 167.6 71.6 96 160 96h72c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H160C98.1 144 48 194.1 48 256s50.1 112 112 112h72c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H160C71.6 416 0 344.4 0 256zm576 0c0 88.4-71.6 160-160 160H344c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24h72c61.9 0 112-50.1 112-112s-50.1-112-112-112H344c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24h72c88.4 0 160 71.6 160 160zM184 232H392c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H184c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24z"></path></svg></div></a></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-hidden pl-8 pr-px"><p class="mt-2 font-semibold prose dark:prose-invert text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200" contentEditable="false" data-component-part="step-title">Implement additional features</p><div data-component-part="step-content" class="prose dark:prose-invert"><span data-as="p">Beyond simply swapping out the base URL, Brandfetch’s Logo API offers powerful features to enhance your logo fetching experience:</span><ul>
<li>
<span data-as="p"><strong>Logo types:</strong> Access not just logo icons, but also brand symbols and main logos.</span>
</li>
<li>
<span data-as="p"><strong>Theme variants:</strong> Access dark or light logos, display them on any background.</span>
</li>
<li>
<span data-as="p"><strong>Customizable sizing:</strong> Adjust the logo’s height and width to fit your needs.</span>
</li>
<li>
<span data-as="p"><strong>Smart fallbacks:</strong> Even when a logo isn’t available, you’ll get fallbacks.</span>
</li>
<li>
<span data-as="p"><strong>Flexible identifiers:</strong> Query directly by domain (e.g., <code>nike.com</code>), Stock or ETF ticker (e.g., <code>NKE</code>, <code>QQQ</code>), ISIN (e.g., <code>US6541061031</code>), or Crypto symbol (e.g., <code>BTC</code>, <code>ETH</code>).</span>
</li>
</ul><span data-as="p">Explore these options in our Logo API <a class="link" href="/logo-api/parameters">parameters page</a>.</span></div></div></div></div>
<hr/>
