 behaviors\",\"description\":\"This section helps you understand different behaviors to expect regarding how Brandfetch sends events to your webhook endpoint.\",\"href\":\"/delivery-methods/webhooks/delivery-behaviors\"},{\"title\":\"Best practices\",\"description\":\"Review these best practices to make sure your webhooks remain secure and function well with your integration.\",\"href\":\"/delivery-methods/webhooks/best-practices\"},{\"title\":\"Event types\",\"description\":\"Overview of subscribable event types\",\"href\":\"/delivery-methods/webhooks/event-types\"}]},{\"title\":\"GraphQL\",\"description\":null,\"href\":\"/delivery-methods/graphql\"}]},{\"group\":\"Support\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Getting help\",\"description\":\"Our support team is always available and willing to assist you.\",\"href\":\"/support/getting-help\"},{\"title\":\"Security \u0026 SOC2\",\"description\":\"Our commitment to secure data handling and best-in-class practices.\",\"href\":\"/support/security-soc2\"},{\"title\":\"Report inaccuracies\",\"url\":\"https://brandfetch.com/update?mode=dev\",\"description\":\"Report incorrect or missing brand info.\",\"href\":\"/support/report-inaccuracies\"},{\"title\":\"Terms and Conditions\",\"url\":\"https://brandfetch.com/terms?mode=dev\",\"description\":null,\"href\":\"/support/terms-and-conditions\"},{\"title\":\"Service status\",\"url\":\"https://status.brandfetch.io\",\"description\":\"Check the status of Brandfetch services.\",\"href\":\"/support/service-status\"}]}]},{\"tab\":\"API References\",\"groups\":[{\"group\":\"Brand API\",\"pages\":[{\"title\":\"Brand API by domain\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"/v2/brands/domain/{domain}\",\"openapi\":\"GET /v2/brands/domain/{domain}\",\"description\":\"Get brand data using a domain name\",\"href\":\"/reference/brand-api-domain\"},{\"title\":\"Brand API by ticker\",\"sidebarTitle\":\"/v2/brands/ticker/{ticker}\",\"openapi\":\"GET /v2/brands/ticker/{ticker}\",\"description\":\"Get brand data using a Stock o